"""
        Test required arguments cannot be skipped.
        """
cmd = '-M model -V vendor'.split(' ')
args = self.parser.parse_args(cmd)
self.assertEqual(str(args),
    "Namespace(destination=None, file=None, ignore_file_type=None, model='model', overwrite=False, source=None, unmatched='ignore', vendor='vendor', verbose=False)"
    )
